{"tid":1426422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你身上一定要有電筒","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:26:50.000Z","uid":295505,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8167d796072f3dcc70520e396ccd8f4f0a271040","tid":1426422,"uid":295505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2015/06/23/flashlight/top-news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2015%2F06%2F23%2Fflashlight%2Ftop-news%2F&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=fbfdbecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2015/06/23/flashlight/top-news/</a><br />\n如何選擇適合自己電筒 ?<br />\n電筒不是流明越高越好，一般使用的 300 流名已很足夠，如果需要很長的照明距離轉用高流明的型號。<strong>太高流明在短距離應用讓眼睛不適甚至太亮看不清楚</strong>，亦大大縮短使用時間，得不償失。要同時擁有高流明及足夠的續航力的話，要用上更大的電池，體積也會增加。在物料方便，<strong>在戰鬥環境使用的可以找尋一些鋼水充足的電筒</strong>，但相對比較重；日常隨身的可挑選輕便物料。總括來說，用家要在體積、重量、流量、續航力幾個元素間作取捨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔用laser point用電筒!!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最強選擇</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameover.com.hk/news/311673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameover.com.hk%2Fnews%2F311673&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=81af139f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameover.com.hk/news/311673</a><br />\n超強電筒 熱到可以生火 照住鑊底炒蛋都得"},{"pid":"793963d558c86f29cd3352c9861dfa709562a597","tid":1426422,"uid":295505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:16:02.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"821f62cdecdc4ab272b1eb584cb867afa4cac08f","tid":1426422,"uid":295505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"d91594970403584cbaffcd7175d58a6f96304abd","tid":1426422,"uid":295505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"bcc8c5b6b6755fedd5b8e89c3113a8d9a9fdead2","tid":1426422,"